author: Fextralife
description:
Clair Obscur Expedition 33 BEHIND THE SCENES - Cast Interviews (Maelle, Verso, Renoir)
We had the chance to sit down with the voice cast of Clair Obscur: Expedition 33. I interviewed Ben Starr, Jennifer English, and Andy Serkis to discuss their roles in this stunning turn-based RPG, their approach to bringing Verso, Maelle, and Renoir to life, and how their performances shape the experience for players. 
If you’re want to hear their thoughts into the world of Clair Obscur Expedition 33, then this is the interview you won’t want to miss.
